         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362"><!-- p4l3-r17 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Hd1e108">Rubrica 17</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De obsequio et resistentia</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>¶ De obsequio et resistentia. Rubrica. 17
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/> <ref>TErentius in andria c. 3</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e125">Hoc tempo
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>re obsequium amicos veritas odi
        <lb ed="#V" n="30" break="no"/>LLum parit.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>
         <ref>¶ Ouidius de arte amandi: li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e137"> Flectitur ob
        <lb ed="#V" n="32" break="no"/>sequio curuatus ab arbore ramus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>Franges: si vires expriare tuas.
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>Obsequio transnantur aque: nec vincere possis
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/> Flumina si contra qua rapit vnda nates
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>Obscquium tigresque domat tumidosque leones</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>
       <ref>/ Idem de remedio amoris: lib. i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e156">Dum furor in cursum est currenti cede furori
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>Difficiles aditus imperus omnis habet
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>Stultus ab obliquo qui cum descendere possis
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Pugnat in aduersas ire natator aquas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
          <ref>¶ Seneca in prouerbiis:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e172">Bonus animus num
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>quam erranti obsequium accommodat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e178">
               <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e182">¶ Ualerius maximus: li. 7. ti. sapienter di
        <lb ed="#V" n="45" break="no"/>cta aut facta: Aristoteles calistenem audito <!--245.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>rem suum ad alexandrum mittens monu
        <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>it cum eo: aut nunquam: aut quamiocundissime lo
        <lb ed="#V" n="48" break="no"/>queretur quo scilicet apud regias aures vel
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>silentior tutior: vel sermone esset acceptior.
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>At illis dum alexandrum macedone gau
        <lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>dente in persica salutatione obiurgat et ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>macedonicos mores inuitum reuocare be
        <lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>niuole perseuerabat spiritum carere iussus: se
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>ram neglecti salubris consilii pniam egit. i </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e212">
               <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>
       <ref>¶ Cecilius firmianus de beaea vita: lib 7: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>fina.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e216">Mores ac vicia regis imitari genus
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>obsequii est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e224">
               <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>
         <ref>¶ Prosper sub. 34. emp.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e228"> Equum est seruire
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>regibus et ducibus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e234">
               <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>
          <ref>¶ Cato capitulo. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e238">Uincere cum possis in.
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>terdum cede sodali. Obsequio quoniam dul
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>ces retinentur amici.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e247">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>
       <ref>¶ Cassiodorus de amincitia. c. 24</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e251">Illud ob
        <lb ed="#V" n="64" break="no"/>sequium dannabile est quod amicum indulgen
        <lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>tiorem viciis facit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e259"> 
          <ref>/ Idem epistolarum: li.
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>3. e. 34.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e261">Libentibus animis obedite: vt si
        <lb ed="#V" n="67" break="no"/>des vestra que iam prioribus monstratur
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>exemplis: subsequentibus quoque declare
        <lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>tur inditiis. Gratius est obsequium quod deuo
        <lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>tione perpeti custoditur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e275">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e279"> <ref>¶ Isydorus in synonima solliloquiorum: li.
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>2. c. 44.</ref> Defer obsequia nil iuxta mores.
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>Facientem et obsequentem par pena con
        <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>stringit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-d1e289">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>
       <ref>¶ Mattheus vindoc. de hysto. tobie. c. 31.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82362-Qd1e293">Obsequio refouetur amor.</quote>
            </p>
